app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/1999-4915/12/3/358/s1, Figure S1: Sampling sites in the far north region near Ahipara, New Zealand, Figure S2: Non-dated phylogeny of Deformed wing virus, Figure S3: Non-dated phylogeny of Kashmir bee virus, Table S1: Primers used for virus detection, Table S2: Sampling location of additional Argentine ant samples used for phylogenetic analyses, Table S3: BaTS analysis of non-dated Deformed wing virus phylogeny, Table S4: BaTS analysis of non-dated Kashmir bee virus phylogeny.
